,{},"這樣子就解決了 Vite for React 中 Tailwind CSS IntelliSense 沒辦法正常運作問題了。",[16,285,286],{},"奇妙的是 CRA(Create React App) 是可以正常跳出 Tailwind CSS IntelliSense，而 Vite 卻不行，所以應該是 Tailwind CSS IntelliSense 套件後來有支援 CRA 吧？我猜。",[12,288,289],{"id":289},"參考文獻",[291,292,293],"ul",{},[294,295,296],"li",{},[164,297,169],{"href":166,"rel":298},[168],[300,301,302],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}",{"title":56,"searchDepth":82,"depth":82,"links":304},[305,306,307,308],{"id":14,"depth":82,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":82,"text":21},{"id":46,"depth":82,"text":46},{"id":289,"depth":82,"text":289},"TailwindCSS","2022-07-02 21:32:31","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Ftailwindcss\u002Fvscode-tailwind-css-intellisense-react-jsx","1",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"TailwindCSS\u002F讓-VSCode-的-Tailwind-CSS-IntelliSense-套件可以用於-React-JSX",[321,322,323,30,324],"Tailwind CSS","Tailwind CSS IntelliSense","VSCode","Create React App",null,"\u002Ftailwindcss\u002F20220702\u002F88023210\u002F","uthZVkpQ_c46gQGyzcu0dk3sDMhPsDU1zjeqiHfz3lQ",{"newer":329,"older":333